** {{ill|Seoritsu-hime|ja|瀬織津姫}} (瀬織津比売) – Carries away all calamities, sins, and impurities to rivers and the sea.
** {{ill|Hayakitsuhiko and Hayakitsuhime|ja|ハヤアキツヒコ・ハヤアキツヒメ}} (速開都比売神) – Awaits at river mouths or the ocean floor to swallow the impurities.
** {{ill|Ibukidonushi|ja|気吹戸主神}} (気吹戸主) – Expels the absorbed impurities to {{ill|Ne-no-kuni|ja|根の国}} (the underworld).
